nk" title="（在新窗口中打开）"><u>夹子</u></a>或<a href="https://zdcs.link/2eMAe?pageview_type=Standard&amp;template=Roundups&amp;module=content-body&amp;element=offer&amp;item=text-link&amp;element_label=ribbon&amp;short_url=2eMAe&amp;u=https%3A%2F%2Flifehacker.com%2Ffeed%2Frss" rel="nofollow sponsored" target="_blank" title="（在新窗口中打开）"><u>丝带</u></a>将艺术品挂在梯级上。将梯子靠在墙上，墙上就不会出现任何洞，您就可以立即进行艺术展示。制作展示架时，请确保您使用的梯子有橡胶脚，以避免损坏地板。 </p><div class="mb-4 rounded-md border-2 border-gray-100 py-7 shadow-xl md:py-6"><div class="order-1 mx-auto flex flex-col justify-center md:order-2 md:ml-4 md:w-full md:grow"><div class="block cursor-pointer text-center font-akshar text-2xl font-medium leading-7 text-brand-green duration-200 ease-in-out hover:text-brand-green-700 md:text-left md:text-xl md:leading-6"> 6 层木制毯子梯子，5.7 英尺（66.5 英寸）毯子被子毛巾架装饰梯，易于组装，乡村农舍梯架，适用于客厅卧室浴室家居装饰，棕色</div><div class="mt-4 hidden md:flex md:justify-between"><div class="self-end"><div class="mb-0 h-11 md:flex md:flex-col md:justify-center"><div class=" font-sans leading-4 text-black"><div class="flex flex-wrap items-center justify-center gap-x-1 md:justify-start"><span class="font-bold"><span class="font-medium">亚马逊</span>46.99 美元</span><img class="mt-0 h-[15px]" src="/images/amazon-prime.svg" title="亚马逊 Prime" alt="Amazon Prime"></div></div></div></div><div class="w-44 self-end"> <button class="flex justify-center items-center w-full bg-brand-green text-white text-base font-sans font-medium rounded-md hover:bg-brand-green-700 hover:cursor-pointer md:text-sm h-11">立即购买</button></div></div></div><div class="order-2 mt-5 h-auto w-full md:order-1 md:mt-0 md:hidden"><div class="flex aspect-video items-center justify-center"><img class="m-0 max-h-full max-w-full rounded-md" src="https://lifehacker.com/imagery/product/072JTrUijH3htYAnzdUZfn6/hero-image.fill.size_autoxauto.v1723177608.jpg" alt="6 层木制毯子梯子，5.7 英尺（66.5 英寸）毯子被子毛巾架装饰梯，易于组装，乡村农舍梯架，适用于客厅卧室浴室家居装饰，棕色" width="auto" height="auto" loading="lazy"></div></div><div class="order-2 ml-2 hidden w-32 shrink-0 items-center md:order-1 md:ml-0 md:flex"><div class="flex aspect-video items-center justify-center"><img class="m-0 max-h-full max-w-full rounded-md" src="https://lifehacker.com/imagery/product/072JTrUijH3htYAnzdUZfn6/hero-image.fill.size_autoxauto.v1723177608.jpg" alt="6 层木制毯子梯子，5.7 英尺（66.5 英寸）毯子被子毛巾架装饰梯，易于组装，乡村农舍梯架，适用于客厅卧室浴室家居装饰，棕色" width="auto" height="auto" loading="lazy"></div></div><div class="order-3 flex grow flex-wrap md:hidden md:grow-0"><div class="mt-4 w-full"> <button class="flex justify-center items-center w-full bg-brand-green text-white text-base font-sans font-medium rounded-md hover:bg-brand-green-700 hover:cursor-pointer md:text-sm h-11">立即购买</button></div><div class="mx-2 mt-4 w-full"><div class=" font-sans leading-4 text-black"><div class="flex flex-wrap items-center justify-center gap-x-1 md:justify-start"><span class="font-bold"><span class="font-medium">亚马逊</span>46.99 美元</span><img class="mt-0 h-[15px]" src="/images/amazon-prime.svg" title="亚马逊 Prime" alt="Amazon Prime"></div></div></div></div></div></div><h2>使用画架</h2><p>如果您有一个较大的作品想要成为焦点，您可以使用<a href="https://zdcs.link/5MvZY?pageview_type=Standard&amp;template=Roundups&amp;module=content-body&amp;element=offer&amp;item=text-link&amp;element_label=an%20easel&amp;short_url=5MvZY&amp;u=https%3A%2F%2Flifehacker.com%2Ffeed%2Frss" rel="nofollow sponsored" target="_blank" title="（在新窗口中打开）"><u>画架</u></a>来展示它。这种展示图片的方法还可以给你的艺术带来一些高度，并使其远离其他家具。一定要测量你的作品，并选择一个适合你想要展示的东西尺寸的画架，这样你的画架就不会翻倒。</p><h2>使用丝带或绳子和窗帘杆</h2><p>对于较轻的照片，您可以从窗帘杆上拉出<a href="https://zdcs.link/6XVl2?pageview_type=Standard&amp;template=Roundups&amp;module=content-body&amp;element=offer&amp;item=text-link&amp;element_label=string&amp;short_url=6XVl2&amp;u=https%3A%2F%2Flifehacker.com%2Ffeed%2Frss" rel="nofollow sponsored" target="_blank" title="（在新窗口中打开）"><u>绳子</u></a>或<a href="https://zdcs.link/4AkrD?pageview_type=Standard&amp;template=Roundups&amp;module=content-body&amp;element=offer&amp;item=text-link&amp;element_label=ribbon&amp;short_url=4AkrD&amp;u=https%3A%2F%2Flifehacker.com%2Ffeed%2Frss" rel="nofollow sponsored" target="_blank" title="（在新窗口中打开）"><u>丝带</u></a>，然后使用<a href="https://zdcs.link/R0lJ7?pageview_type=Standard&amp;template=Roundups&amp;module=content-body&amp;element=offer&amp;item=text-link&amp;element_label=clothespins&amp;short_url=R0lJ7&amp;u=https%3A%2F%2Flifehacker.com%2Ffeed%2Frss" rel="nofollow sponsored" target="_blank" title="（在新窗口中打开）"><u>衣夹</u></a>或<a href="https://zdcs.link/AdGK0?pageview_type=Standard&amp;template=Roundups&amp;module=content-body&amp;element=offer&amp;item=text-link&amp;element_label=binder%20clips&amp;short_url=AdGK0&amp;u=https%3A%2F%2Flifehacker.com%2Ffeed%2Frss" rel="nofollow sponsored" target="_blank" title="（在新窗口中打开）"><u>活页夹</u></a>来固定照片。您也可以选择垂直悬挂丝带或绳子，尽管您需要将环系到丝带或绳子上以便为夹子提供固定点。这种展示方式仅适用于无框图片，因为框架对于窗帘杆和夹子来说可能太重。</p><h2>倾斜布告栏</h2><p>如果您有一个大<a href="https://zdcs.link/0Pd5w?pageview_type=Standard&amp;template=Roundups&amp;module=content-body&amp;element=offer&amp;item=text-link&amp;element_label=bulletin%20board&amp;short_url=0Pd5w&amp;u=https%3A%2F%2Flifehacker.com%2Ffeed%2Frss" rel="nofollow sponsored" target="_blank" title="（在新窗口中打开）"><u>公告板</u></a>，您可以将其靠在桌子或梳妆台上，然后用<a href="https://zdcs.link/W0AqA?pageview_type=Standard&amp;template=Roundups&amp;module=content-body&amp;element=offer&amp;item=text-link&amp;element_label=push%20pins&amp;short_url=W0AqA&amp;u=https%3A%2F%2Flifehacker.com%2Ffeed%2Frss" rel="nofollow sponsored" target="_blank" title="（在新窗口中打开）"><u>图钉</u></a>将您的艺术作品添加到其中，从而将其变成照片展示。您可能只想对打印件执行此操作，因为您将用大头钉在纸张上打孔。如果您想使用公告板方法而不在纸张上打孔，您可以使用<a href="https://zdcs.link/W0g37?pageview_type=Standard&amp;template=Roundups&amp;module=content-body&amp;element=offer&amp;item=text-link&amp;element_label=push%20pins%20with%20clips&amp;short_url=W0g37&amp;u=https%3A%2F%2Flifehacker.com%2Ffeed%2Frss" rel="nofollow sponsored" target="_blank" title="（在新窗口中打开）"><u>带夹子的图钉</u></a>来悬挂无框的照片和艺术品。 </p><div class="mb-4 rounded-md border-2